Enhancement: `restic check`, `restic repair packs` now  heal lost packfiles

In the past, deleted packfiles could not be repaired with the `restic check` and
`restic repair packs` command, since a missing packfile triggered an error exit
and not the repair procedure.

these commands now treat missing packfiles the same way as
damaged packfiles are treated. These conditions can now repaired correctly.

